      <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb"><ol><li><a href="/">Home</a></li><li aria-current="page">Emergency</li></ol></nav><figure class="page-hero"><div class="page-hero__media"><img src="/Past_work_webp/Service%20after.webp" width="1536" height="2048" alt="Electrical service repair completed with upgraded meter equipment" decoding="async" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high"></div></figure><section class="page-hero">
