    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">Urgent electrical concerns</span>
      <h1>
        When something feels unsafe, unstable, or actively disruptive, the next
        step should be simple.
      </h1>
      <p class="lead-copy">
        If you smell burning, have visible arcing, repeated breaker failure,
        partial power loss, water exposure, or equipment that seems unsafe, call
        or text directly. Do not rely on a standard form submission for
        time-sensitive electrical concerns.
      </p>
      <div class="badge-row">
        <span class="badge">Call or text for urgent issues</span
        ><span class="badge">Shut off affected equipment when safe</span>
